    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《Top Burger Shop》中，准备美味的汉堡，满足饥饿的顾客，在充满活力、节奏快的环境中经营你的店铺！管理你的店铺，解锁新食材，并在180个关卡中挑战有趣的任务。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/71358c5585505f4eb33c32965688cae4.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.poster.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.webm?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/ba54371c94caed3022a912038b249eb8.mp4?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于《Top Burger Shop》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Top Burger Shop Simulator》中，成为一名汉堡大师，制作美味的食物来满足饥饿的顾客。管理你的店铺，同时解锁新的食材和角色，面对有趣的挑战，考验你的烹饪技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/934f193dd1392b47c2cb57e9760da5a9.webp?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.poster.avif?t=1772361310\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.webm?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310020/extras/75737d2c62f48155ee80a9a733c8b808.mp4?t=1772361310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索三个世界，面对独特的挑战，共180个关卡。利用激动人心的道具：自动提示、金币磁铁和顾客快乐时光。选择21个迷人的动画角色，并在游戏进程中解锁新食材和道具。享受三种游戏模式——厨师冠军、职业生涯和时间攻击——进行一场美味的冒险！</p>",
